source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_00<tab>Isaudorel's companion has been taciturn till now, but when Ireine has something to say, all present are advised to listen.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_00<tab>神勇隊「白羊師団」のイレヌは、冒険者に伝令の仕事を頼みたいようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_01<tab>Overhearing your conversation with Isaudorel, Ireine bids you take Coerthas' Ixal problem up the chain of command. Leave Ireine and Isaudorel to hurl comradely abuse at one another and make your report to Miah Molkot at Eugenia's Spire.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_01<tab>クルザスでのイクサル族問題を解決するには、作戦を練ったほうがいいということだ。ユージニア監視哨にいる白羊師団の師団長「ミア・モルコット」に、状況を報告しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_02<tab>Miah Molkot accepts Belmont's request without demur and with much purr. You learn that the White Rams are in fact a counter-Ixal levy, and on a personal level, Molkot appears to take nearly gustatory delight in defeating the birdmen.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_SEQ_02<tab>ミア・モルコットは、ベルモントからの依頼に賛同してくれた。彼女によれば、白羊師団はグリダニアの擁する神勇隊の中でも、イクサル族との戦闘に特化した部隊らしい。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_000<tab>Well met, adventurer. May I call you <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>? I'm Ireine, a tactical officer of the White Rams─and apparently a medic, for I find myself ordered to keep an eye on this lug. Oh, shut it, Isaudorel!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_000<tab>私はイレヌ。
神勇隊「白羊師団」の参謀……兼、衛生兵よ。
団員が怪我しちゃったから付き添ってるところなの。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_001<tab>So, the matter you were speaking to Isaudorel about. I'm certain Instructor Molkot will be keen to hear of the Ixal's movements in the west─best you talk to her straightaway and make plans.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_001<tab>……ところでイゾドレールとの会話、横で聞かせてもらったわ。
そのイクサル族の話、ちゃんと私たちの師団長に伝えて、
作戦を練ったほうがいいわね。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_002<tab>That'd be Miah Molkot, the leader of the White Rams and an instructor of the Gods' Quiver. She bides this day at Eugenia's Spire to the north. Take Belmont's words to her.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_002<tab>白羊師団を率いる「ミア・モルコット」師団長は、
現在、北の「ユージニア監視哨」で任務遂行中なの。
行って報告をお願いするわ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_003<tab>And do watch yourself. Miah Molkot's slain as many Ixal in battle as there are trees in the woods of Proud Creek. She can be...scary. Waste her time with maffles or bluster, and she might use you as Ixal bait.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_IREINE_000_003<tab>モルコット師団長は、これまでの戦いで、
プラウドクリークの森の木の数ほどイクサル族を討伐した
歴戦の勇者……恐ろしいわよ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_MIAHMOLKOT_000_010<tab>Who scratches at my door? An adventurer on the prowl for Miah Molkot? I am she, born to be the bane of the birdmen! I lead the White Rams, an arrow of the Gods' Quiver aimed at the craven hearts of the Ixal.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_MIAHMOLKOT_000_010<tab>ニャニャ！？　冒険者がニャんの用だ？
私が神勇隊、対イクサル族特務戦闘部隊、
通称「白羊師団」の師団長、ミア・モルコットだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_MIAHMOLKOT_000_011<tab>I see! We must act now─right <var 1A 02 /var>now<var 1A 01 /var>─to stop this threat. Extending the defensive line against the Ixal northwest into Coerthas will be no stroll through the wood, but ah, how the birdies will struggle in the net! I can already hear their little necks breaking...
target:
TEXT_GAIUSB712_00907_MIAHMOLKOT_000_011<tab>……ニャるほど、状況は理解した。
クルザスと黒衣森の「対イクサル族防衛線」の構築か……
協力するに、やぶさかではニャい。喜んで引き受けよう。
